description: This file declares the interface functions for the Slap Var Entity Object in the Service Logic Aggregation Plane (SLAP). It includes creation, removal, object mapping, and initialization functions used internally within the module. The file defines the exported API for other components to interact with the Slap Var Entity Object.

methods.name: SlapCreateVarEntity
methods.description: Creates a new Slap Var Entity object with specified container and owner contexts.

methods.name: SlapVeoGetSlapObjCallMap
methods.description: Retrieves the call map for the Slap Var Entity Object.

methods.name: SlapVeoGetSlapObjDescriptor
methods.description: Retrieves the descriptor for the Slap Var Entity Object.

methods.name: SlapVeoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Slap Var Entity Object.

methods.name: SlapVeoRemove
methods.description: Removes and cleans up an instance of the Slap Var Entity Object.

methods.name: SlapVeoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls and initializes objects within the Slap Var Entity Object.

methods.name: SlapVeoInitialize
methods.description: Performs initialization routines for the Slap Var Entity Object.
